profile:
About Our Moving Company in Lethbridge
 Neighbourhood Movers is a family owned Lethbridge moving company with a combined experience of 37 years. The owner, Rob, has been in the business for 16 years. Our experience allows us to handle a variety of local and long distance moving scenarios for residential and commercial clients. We offer free estimates and a professional consultation for all moves at Neighbourhood Movers. When you schedule a consultation, we will meet with you to discuss your specific moving needs, tailoring our moving service to fit you. Our movers are professional and fully insured. 

A Worry-Free Moving Company
 Moving from home to home or office to office can be a stressful time no matter where you’re relocating. That’s why Neighbourhood Movers is the moving company Lethbridge trusts to make their local or long distance moves worry and hassle free. Our movers will break down and set up furniture, taking pains to ensure everything arrives safe and undamaged. Our courteous, reliable, and clean staff members have the knowledge and experience to handle all your residential and office moving needs. 

Free Estimates from Our Lethbridge Moving Company
Neighbourhood Movers offers timely local and long distance service, with no minimum. We make weekly runs to Calgary, Edmonton, Vancouver, and all cities in between; give us a call at 403-331-9176 for a free estimate.
project_minimum: No job is too small or big
